org.eyedb
Class Database

java.lang.Object
  org.eyedb.Object
      org.eyedb.Instance
          org.eyedb.Agregat
              org.eyedb.Struct
                  org.eyedb.Database

public class Database
extends Struct

This class is used to open a database and to perform operations on it.

For instance : 

 Database db = new Database("mydatabase");

 try {
   db.open(conn, Database.DBRead);
 } catch(Exception e) {
   System.err.println(e);
   System.exit(1);
 }
